==English==

===Etymology===
[[Portmanteau word]] of '''[[gigantic]]''' and '''[[enormous]]'''.

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}

# Very [[big]].
#:''He drove up in a '''ginormous''' [[stretch limo]].''
#:''That [[apple]] was '''ginormous'''!''

